The boy has a new hobby... sending me tells<br>
<br>
&quot;hEY&quot;<br>
&quot;hI&quot;<br>
&quot;LOL&quot;<br>
&quot;iTs me! FeStT!&quot;<br>
&quot;LOL&quot;<br>
