<br>
Since that day... ive gotten messages from 13 different characters (none of them ever more than level 2) with more of the same dribble...<br>
<br>
Im under constant spam assult... and as quickly as I can /ignore him... hes making a new character...<br>
<br>
Not that its really bugging me... but <br>
<br>
1) Would it be silly if I petitioned about somthing that is annoying at best<br>
2) Who would pay for everquest just to send people pointless spam?<br>
3) Is there anything I can do besides /ignoring? I dont want to be mean or anything... but the chatter... it has no substance... and when fighting.. there is more purple spam from this guy than there are combat messages<br>
<br>
I really dont mind talking to people in EQ... infact... its why I play... I love the people... but this is runing my fun.. and I dont know what to do.<br>
<br>
The comics will come.... <br>
